00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:42.960
to even dust off your shoes.

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:45.600
Lift the carriage.

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.240
Return to the palace.

00:00:53.560 --> 00:00:54.680
Who do you think you are

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:56.040
to walk beside Her Highness?

00:00:56.240 --> 00:00:57.280
Get to the back!

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:12.320
(Chengxi Palace)

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:14.440
Starting today,

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.240
you shall serve
as Chengxi Palace's cleaning maid.

00:01:17.470 --> 00:01:18.300
Remember.

00:01:18.680 --> 00:01:20.280
You can only do courtyard cleaning.

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:21.400
No entry to halls.

00:01:21.960 --> 00:01:23.280
Learn the rules properly

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:25.320
and fulfill your basic duties.

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:26.720
I

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:28.920
was personally selected by Her Highness.

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:31.680
Why assign me to cleaning duty,

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:33.360
such a simple task?

00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:35.760
What? Do you find it beneath you?

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:40.040
Chengxi Palace is the imperial harem's
most prestigious residence.

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:42.680
People are dying to get in.

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:44.200
Yet you show ingratitude?

00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:47.120
Being a Chengxi Palace cleaning maid

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:49.360
is a fortune earned
through lifetimes of virtue.

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:51.480
Know your place

00:01:51.800 --> 00:01:53.120
and do your duties.

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:56.640
If you break our palace's rules,

00:01:57.400 --> 00:01:58.800
you'll forfeit your pathetic life.

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:00.832
Understood.

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:02.720
I heed your instructions.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:04.608
Hmph!

00:02:10.899 --> 00:02:13.216
(Chengxi Palace)

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:21.200
- We congratulate Your Highness on the coronation.
- We congratulate Your Highness on the coronation.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:22.600
- For Your Highness,
- For Your Highness,

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:23.960
- may blessings flow endlessly,
- may blessings flow endlessly,

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:25.480
- imperial favor endure forever,
- imperial favor endure forever,

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:26.880
- joy persist through ages,
- joy persist through ages,

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:28.560
- and majesty bloom eternally.
- and majesty bloom eternally.

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:36.768
Be seated.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:38.240
- Thank you, Your Highness.
- Thank you, Your Highness.

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:43.440
Congratulations.

00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:45.360
The coronation ceremony is grand.

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:49.160
It truly reflects His Majesty's
unique favor towards you.

00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:50.960
How we envy such distinction.

00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:53.040
Your celestial beauty

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:55.440
ensures His Majesty's lasting affection.

00:02:55.640 --> 00:02:57.400
Such fortune exceeds our humble hopes.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:59.400
Your Highness's lasting youth

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:00.320
ensures endless favors.

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:01.880
Henceforth we must

00:03:02.320 --> 00:03:03.800
rely on Your Highness's guidance.

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:05.200
Well said.

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:07.680
To retain imperial favor,

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:09.680
one must master beauty preservation.

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:12.760
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

00:03:12.920 --> 00:03:15.120
- May endless fortune bless you.
- May endless fortune bless you.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:25.520
Consort Wan, your management duty
over the Six Palaces must be exhausting.

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:28.240
Today I notice your complexion

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:29.920
appears distressingly haggard.

00:03:30.800 --> 00:03:32.040
How fortuitous.

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:34.440
